tates, as wellas nationally.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BeforeBidenstepped aside,Trumphad led polling in every key swing state:Arizona, Georgia, Michigan Wisconsin,Pennsylvania,North Carolina, andNevada.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"score\": 0.9999900221907703, \"rank\": 7.538309761184988e-06, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\"}, {\"begin\": 2633, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"score\": 0.6853276873284243, \"rank\": 0.26517882366481954, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\"}, {\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"score\": 0.9999118389031644, \"rank\": 8.556717969729177e-05, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan\"}, {\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wisconsin\", \"score\": 0.9999994890091726, \"rank\": 3.7963769403600364e-07, \"text\": \"Wisconsin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wisconsin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wisconsin\"}, {\"begin\": 2661, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9981987292592774, \"rank\": 0.0018023549680619923, \"text\": \"Pennsylvania\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\"}, {\"begin\": 2674, \"end\": 2688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina\", \"score\": 